@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Core Document Operations (Open, Edit, Save)
actor User
participant "UI (DocumentEditorActivity/ExcelEditorActivity)" as UI
participant "Local File System" as LFS
participant "Document Processing Engine" as Engine

== Open Document ==
User -> UI : Select File
UI -> LFS : Read file URI
activate LFS
LFS --> UI : File Stream
deactivate LFS
UI -> Engine : Parse Document (Word/Excel)
activate Engine
Engine --> UI : Document Model
deactivate Engine
UI --> User : Render Document

== Edit Document ==
User -> UI : Type text / format / edit cell
UI -> Engine : Update Document Model
Engine --> UI : Acknowledge Update
UI --> User : Update UI View

== Save Document ==
User -> UI : Click "Save"
UI -> Engine : Generate File Output Stream
activate Engine
Engine --> UI : Byte Stream
deactivate Engine
UI -> LFS : Write to file URI
activate LFS
LFS --> UI : Success Confirmation
deactivate LFS
UI --> User : Show "Saved Successfully"

@enduml
